title: Can't find Winter's Presence in skins API

comments.author: Chiuna.2538
comments.body: Oh, I had no idea! I thought I might have had the wrong id numbers or was overlooking something. Thanks for doing the clicking, I hope you are feeling better now!

comments.author: Lawton Campbell.8517
comments.body: All the items/skins/recipes are behind a manual whitelisting step (e.g., I have to click a button before they appear) and I’ve been out sick since mid last week. They should start appearing this morning <3

comments.author: Chiuna.2538
comments.body: Is the skins API missing some items? I’m trying to find the new Winter’s Presence skins and the wiki shows their IDs as 6577, 6583, and 6586 but I can’t find info about them with either v1 or v2 of the API.
